My very own personal and basic setup for my VIM environment.

Now includes pathogen so that the installation of new plugins should be easier.

References:
http://vimcasts.org/episodes/synchronizing-plugins-with-git-submodules-and-pathogen/
http://biodegradablegeek.com/2007/12/using-vim-as-a-complete-ruby-on-rails-ide/
http://www.adamlowe.me/2009/12/vim-destroys-all-other-rails-editors.html
http://www.akitaonrails.com/2009/01/04/rails-on-vim-in-english

Plugins:
http://github.com/scrooloose/nerdtree
http://github.com/tpope/vim-rails
http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2004

Installation
git clone {repository} ~/.vim
ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc .vimrc
git submodule init
git submodule update
